--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-11-13)
C: Remove option promtail_pipeline_stages
F: Add options promtail_pipeline_stages_(all|group|host)

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-11-08)
B: Correct default listen port
E: Add reload capability to systemd service unit file

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-11-06)
F: Initial release
